etsysNacApplianceMIB.name: etsysNacApplianceMIB

revisions.description: The initial version of this MIB module.

etsysNacApplianceMIB.contactinfo: Postal: Enterasys Networks 50 Minuteman Rd. Andover, MA 01810-1008 USA Phone: +1 978 684 1000 E-mail: support@enterasys.com WWW: http://www.enterasys.com
etsysNacApplianceMIB.description: This MIB module defines a portion of the SNMP enterprise MIBs under Enterasys Networks' enterprise OID pertaining to NAC Appliance Status.

etsysNacApplAuthenticationRequests.name: etsysNacApplAuthenticationRequests
etsysNacApplAuthenticationRequests.description: Represents the number of authentication requests made since the NAC was started.

etsysNacApplAuthenticationSuccesses.name: etsysNacApplAuthenticationSuccesses
etsysNacApplAuthenticationSuccesses.description: Represents the number of successful authentication requests made since the NAC was started.

etsysNacApplAuthenticationFailures.name: etsysNacApplAuthenticationFailures
etsysNacApplAuthenticationFailures.description: Represents the number of failed authentication requests made since the NAC was started.

etsysNacApplRadiusChallenges.name: etsysNacApplRadiusChallenges
etsysNacApplRadiusChallenges.description: Represents the number of Radius challenges made since the NAC was started.

etsysNacApplAuthenticationInvalidRequest.name: etsysNacApplAuthenticationInvalidRequests
etsysNacApplAuthenticationInvalidRequest.description: Represents the number of invalid authentication requests made since the NAC was started.

etsysNacApplAuthenticationDuplicateReque.name: etsysNacApplAuthenticationDuplicateRequests
etsysNacApplAuthenticationDuplicateReque.description: Represents the number of duplicate authentication requests made since the NAC was started.

etsysNacApplAuthenticationMalformedReque.name: etsysNacApplAuthenticationMalformedRequests
etsysNacApplAuthenticationMalformedReque.description: Represents the number of malformed authentication requests made since the NAC was started.

etsysNacApplAuthenticationBadRequests.name: etsysNacApplAuthenticationBadRequests
etsysNacApplAuthenticationBadRequests.description: Represents the number of bad authentication requests made since the NAC was started.

etsysNacApplAuthenticationDroppedPackets.name: etsysNacApplAuthenticationDroppedPackets
etsysNacApplAuthenticationDroppedPackets.description: Represents the number of dropped authentication packets since the NAC was started.

etsysNacApplAuthenticationUnknownTypes.name: etsysNacApplAuthenticationUnknownTypes
etsysNacApplAuthenticationUnknownTypes.description: Represents the number of unknown authentication types since the NAC was started.

etsysNacApplAssessmentRequests.name: etsysNacApplAssessmentRequests
etsysNacApplAssessmentRequests.description: Represents the number of assessment requests made since the NAC was started.

etsysNacApplCaptivePortalRequests.name: etsysNacApplCaptivePortalRequests
etsysNacApplCaptivePortalRequests.description: Represents the number of captive portal requests made since the NAC was started.

etsysNacApplContactLostSwitches.name: etsysNacApplContactLostSwitches
etsysNacApplContactLostSwitches.description: Represents the number of configured switches with which the NAC has lost SNMP contact.

etsysNacApplIPResolutionFailures.name: etsysNacApplIPResolutionFailures
etsysNacApplIPResolutionFailures.description: Represents the number of failed IP Resolution attempts made since the NAC was started.

etsysNacApplIPResolutionTimeouts.name: etsysNacApplIPResolutionTimeouts
etsysNacApplIPResolutionTimeouts.description: Represents the number of IP Resolution attempts that timed out since the NAC was started.

etsysNacApplConnectedAgents.name: etsysNacApplConnectedAgents
etsysNacApplConnectedAgents.description: Represents the number of End-System Assessment Agents currently connected to the NAC.

etsysNacApplianceMIBGroup.name: etsysNacApplianceMIBGroup
etsysNacApplianceMIBGroup.description: The basic collection of objects providing status information about the NAC Appliance.
